Cost-effectiveness of enfuvirtide for treatment-experienced patients with HIV in 
Italy.

Hornberger J(1), Green J, Wintfeld N, Cavassini M, Rockstroh J, Giuliani G, De 
Carli C, Lazzarin A.

Author information:
(1)The SPHERE Institute / Acumen, LLC, 1415 Rollins Road, Suite 110, Burlingame, 
