regimen delays virological failure (VF), reduces HIV-1 viral load, and increases 
CD4 count compared with OB only in pretreated patients.
PURPOSE: To forecast long-term outcomes, costs, and cost-effectiveness of ENF+OB 
vs. OB in the Italian health care system.
METHOD: A Markov model was developed and clinical trial results on viral 
suppression and CD4 count were linked with data from HAART-era studies of the 
